rules_text:
{W}{U} CONTROL The underworld is yours to dictate. Carve out your heinous throne.
{U}{B} UNDERWORLD CREATURES Traverse the dark circles of Bocacius in search of sin.
{B}{R} HELLSPAWN Gather Demons and Devils to rule the damned.
{R}{G} FEROCIOUS  In the freezing depths of the underworld, true strength is all that matters.
{G}{W} PENANCE TOUGHNESS Repent your sins by embracing your endurance. 
{W}{B} UNEARTH Dig foul magicks and relics from the infernal muck.
{B}{G} UNEARTH The restless damned cry out for a second chance.
{G}{U} DESCEND Reach deep into the abyss and find power.
{U}{R} UNDERWORLD SPELLS Sinful magicks secure your place in the underworld.
{R}{W} PENANCE POWER Might makes right. Purge your guilt through a strong offense.
